dn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/101802/72/1018027231_0:19:1000:582_1920x0_80_0_0_ae9cd7d85a8fe2dd6c9fd6b0b19fee66.jpg 1920w" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></div></div><div class="media__copyright " data-nosnippet=""><div class="media__copyright-item m-copyright"> © Sipa Press/Rex Features </div></div></div></div><div class="article__messengers"><div class="flex-align_center"><span class="article__google-news__label"></span></div><div class="flex-align_center"></div><div class="article__telegram-news flex-align_center"><span class="article__google-news__label">订阅</span></div><div class="flex-align_center"><div class="article__telegram-button"><a href="https://t.me/SputnikInt" title="国际的" class="" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">国际的</a></div><div class="article__telegram-button"><a href="https://telegram.me/sputniknewsindia" title="印度" class="" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">印度</a></div><div class="article__telegram-button"><a href="https://t.me/sputnik_africa" title="非洲" class="" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">非洲</a></div></div></div><div class="article__author"><div class="article__author-item"><div class="article__author-wrapper"><div class="article__author-image"><img media-type="ar1x1" data-source-sid="" alt=" - Sputnik International" title="" src="https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e6/01/0b/1092187887_0:0:2048:2049_100x100_80_0_0_0c2cc4c84f89aff034cc55bb01fb6697.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></div><div class="article__author-info"><div class="article__author-name">玛丽·曼利</div><div class="article__author-links"><a class="m-color-main" href="https://sputniknews.com/author_manley_mary/" title="所有材料">所有材料</a></div></div></div></div></div><div class="article__announce-text">周四，摩根大通在一份法庭文件中指责塞西尔·德容 (Cecile de Jongh) 是爱泼斯坦“在整个 USVI 政府传播金钱和影响力的主要渠道”。 </div></div><div class="article__body"><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">世界上最大的银行之一指控美属维尔京群岛 (USVI) 前州长的妻子协助杰弗里·爱泼斯坦 (Jeffrey Epstein) 的性犯罪。塞西尔·德容 (Cecile de Jongh) 的娘家姓是塞西尔·加利伯 (Cecile Galiber)，她是维尔京群岛的前第一夫人，她在 2007 年至 2015 年担任该职位，当时她的丈夫是州长。 </div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="vrez"><div class="article__vrez"><div class="article__vrez-text"><p>塞西尔为爱泼斯坦工作，爱泼斯坦是一名美国金融家，他因拉拢儿童卖淫和贩卖儿童而被捕，但在等待审判期间自杀身亡。据摩根大通称，她在 USVI 管理爱泼斯坦的公司，仅在 2007 年就获得了 20 万美元的报酬。</p><p>爱泼斯坦在世时在美属维尔京群岛拥有一座小岛。</p></div></div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">摩根大通还声称，爱泼斯坦支付了前第一夫人子女的学费，因为她向爱泼斯坦提供了<strong>“如何购买对 USVI 政治阶层的控制权”的建议。</strong> </div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="quote"><div class="article__quote"><div class="article__quote-text">摩根大通在法庭<u><a href="https://assets.bwbx.io/documents/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/r.ELbMd_4s4U/v0" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener">文件</a></u>中说：“二十年来，爱泼斯坦与 USVI 的最高官员保持着交换关系。他给了他们金钱、建议、影响力和好处。作为交换，他们保护甚至奖励他。 ” </div><div class="article__quote-info"><div class="elem-info"><div class="elem-info__share"><div class="share" data-id="1110619337" data-url="https://sputnikglobe.com/20230526/jpmorgan-claims-wife-of-ex-virgin-islands-governor-aided-jeffrey-epsteins-crimes-1110619337.html?share-block=1110619875" data-title="&quot;For two decades, Epstein maintained a quid pro quo relationship with USVI’s highest ranking officials,” the JPMorgan said in the court document. “He gave them money, advice, influence, and favors. In exchange, they shielded and even rewarded him.”"></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text"> USVI 去年对该银行提起民事诉讼，指控摩根大通<strong>“对爱泼斯坦走私企业的运作和隐瞒不可或缺”。</strong>他们对 Cecile 的指控是对诉讼的回应的一部分，该诉讼正在寻求银行的金钱赔偿。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">该银行还声称，塞西尔帮助爱泼斯坦为他的受害者获得学生签证，并帮助他们注册维尔京群岛大学的“定制班”，该大学的创建是为了“为他们在该地区的存在提供掩护”。在他们“入学”的同一年，爱泼斯坦通过他的一家公司向大学捐赠了 20,000 美元。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text"><strong>该文件补充说，塞西尔建议爱泼斯坦让其他人在受害者的学校付款信上签字，因为她可能“意识到让登记在案的性犯罪者在信上签字的风险”。</strong></div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">爱泼斯坦还会见了美属维尔京群岛港务局的领导层，该机构在圣托马斯岛经营着一个机场，据称爱泼斯坦在那里贩运了他的受害者。据报道，塞西尔要求爱泼斯坦支持当地立法者重返港务局的职位，因为对他来说，担任该职位对他来说是个好人选。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">文件显示，爱泼斯坦向美属维尔京群岛政客和政府捐赠了大量资金，其中包括向自 2015 年以来担任美国众议院代表的 Stacey Plaskett 的竞选活动捐赠了 30,000 美元，向现任州长 Albert Bryan 的就职委员会捐赠了 25,000 美元，并向学校图书馆捐赠了 25,000 美元。 </div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="quote"><div class="article__quote"><div class="article__quote-text">法庭文件称：“根据他与政府的关系，当作为登记在册的性犯罪者在年轻女性的陪同下穿越美属维尔京群岛机场时，爱泼斯坦可以依靠他与那里官员的‘良好关系’来避免审查或侦查。” </div><div class="article__quote-info"><div class="elem-info"><div class="elem-info__share"><div class="share" data-id="1110619337" data-url="https://sputnikglobe.com/20230526/jpmorgan-claims-wife-of-ex-virgin-islands-governor-aided-jeffrey-epsteins-crimes-1110619337.html?share-block=1110619877" data-title="“Based on his government connections, when traveling through the USVI’s airport accompanied by young women as a registered sex offender, Epstein could count on his ‘great relationship’ with the officials there to avoid scrutiny or detection,” the court document said."></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">该文件还发现， <u><a href="https://fortune.com/2023/05/25/jpmorgan-jeffrey-epstein-virgin-islands-first-lady-sex-trafficking-de-jongh/" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener">2010 年</a></u>，爱泼斯坦给塞西尔发了电子邮件，向她抱怨机场的海关官员“难相处”。然后，两年后，他询问是否要在感恩节给所有 78 名机场官员送火鸡。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text"> 2011 年，塞西尔还联系了爱泼斯坦，以确保提议加强对性犯罪者的监控的立法法案的措辞“对他有用”。然后，当法案通过时，她为“事情的结果”向他道歉。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text"> <a href="https://www.nbcnews.com/news/us-news/jpmorgan-alleges-ex-virgin-islands-first-lady-aided-jeffrey-epstein-rcna86365" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener">报道</a>表明，塞西尔尚未对该文件发表评论。</div></div></div> ]]>;</description><pubDate> Fri, 26 May 2023 23:06:22 GMT</pubDate><guid ispermalink="false"> https://sputniknews.com/20230526/jpmorgan-claims-wife-of-ex-virgin-islands-governor-aided-jeffrey-epsteins-crimes-1110619337.html</guid><link/> https://sputniknews.com/20230526/jpmorgan-claims-wife-of-ex-virgin-islands-governor-aided-jeffrey-epsteins-crimes-1110619337.html<category>美洲</category><category>杰弗里·爱泼斯坦</category><category>性交易</category><category>维尔京群岛</category><category>诉讼</category><category>摩根大通</category></item><item><title><![CDATA[FBI Reveals 1983 Plot to Assassinate Queen Elizabeth II During US Visit]]></title><description><![CDATA[<div class="article__header"><div class="article__announce"><div class="media" data-media-tipe="ar16x9"><div class="media__size"><div class="photoview__open" data-photoview-group="1110618206" data-photoview-src="https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e7/05/1a/1110618448_0:0:1225:1000_1440x900_80_0_1_e1997b8c1c56eac9e79d50181f4b0272.jpg?source-sid=cc_0" data-photoview-image-id="1110618430" data-photoview-sharelink="https://sputnikglobe.com/20230526/fbi-reveals-1983-plot-to-assassinate-queen-elizabeth-ii-during-us-visit-1110618206.html?share-img=1110618430"><noindex><div class="photoview__open-info"> <span class="photoview__copyright"><a href="https://creativecommons.org/publicdomain/zero/1.0/" title="CC0">CC0</a> / <a href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/30484128@N03/" title="吉姆格里芬">Jim Griffin</a> / <a href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/30484128@N03/52344193609/in/photolist-2nKtF7H-2mSawwH-x4ropK-k1H7g-a4EoTn-2m3WG8D-HgJFPv-LQZu9H-HWL1jh-dBxp5T-VUpg1d-dVXHdP-Hr99wZ-JkQgKc-JdfV5J-PMmEkB-NwKfWJ-JjhWPE-PBdihg-PyDhob-PBdjE6-dBxMwD-JdimVN-HwtpuB-W2dGHB" title="优胜美地的伊丽莎白女王——1983 年">伊丽莎白女王在优胜美地 - 1983 年</a></span><span class="photoview__desc-text">洛杉矶时报的一张纪念照片。</span> </div></noindex><img media-type="ar16x9" data-source-sid="cc_0" alt="A memorial photo in the Los Angeles Times. - Sputnik International, 1920, 26.05.2023" title="《洛杉矶时报》的一张纪念照片。" src="https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e7/05/1a/1110618448_0:311:1225:1000_1920x0_80_0_0_d79429f387e48c2b7e9649b073f3013e.jpg" decoding="async" width="1920" height="1080" srcset="https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e7/05/1a/1110618448_0:311:1225:1000_640x0_80_0_0_e8aff81fa95cc24bbfcb3d891e6ed111.jpg 640w,https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e7/05/1a/1110618448_0:311:1225:1000_1280x0_80_0_0_742865b987650d4f7b3835f1b70c1625.jpg 1280w,https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e7/05/1a/1110618448_0:311:1225:1000_1920x0_80_0_0_d79429f387e48c2b7e9649b073f3013e.jpg 1920w" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></div></div><div class="media__copyright " data-nosnippet=""><div class="media__copyright-item m-copyright"> <a href="https://creativecommons.org/publicdomain/zero/1.0/" title="CC0">CC0</a> / <a href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/30484128@N03/" title="吉姆格里芬">Jim Griffin</a> / <a href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/30484128@N03/52344193609/in/photolist-2nKtF7H-2mSawwH-x4ropK-k1H7g-a4EoTn-2m3WG8D-HgJFPv-LQZu9H-HWL1jh-dBxp5T-VUpg1d-dVXHdP-Hr99wZ-JkQgKc-JdfV5J-PMmEkB-NwKfWJ-JjhWPE-PBdihg-PyDhob-PBdjE6-dBxMwD-JdimVN-HwtpuB-W2dGHB" title="优胜美地的伊丽莎白女王——1983 年">优胜美地的伊丽莎白女王 -- 1983</a> </div></div></div></div><div class="article__messengers"><div class="flex-align_center"><span class="article__google-news__label"></span></div><div class="flex-align_center"></div><div class="article__telegram-news flex-align_center"><span class="article__google-news__label">订阅</span></div><div class="flex-align_center"><div class="article__telegram-button"><a href="https://t.me/SputnikInt" title="国际的" class="" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">国际的</a></div><div class="article__telegram-button"><a href="https://telegram.me/sputniknewsindia" title="印度" class="" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">印度</a></div><div class="article__telegram-button"><a href="https://t.me/sputnik_africa" title="非洲" class="" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">非洲</a></div></div></div><div class="article__author"><div class="article__author-item"><div class="article__author-wrapper"><div class="article__author-info"><div class="article__author-name">叶戈尔·沙波瓦洛夫</div><div class="article__author-links"><a class="m-color-main" href="https://sputniknews.com/author_shapovalov_egor/" title="所有材料">所有材料</a><a data-modal-open="feedback_author" href="mailto:e.shapovalov@sputniknews.com" title="写给作者">写给作者</a></div></div></div></div></div><div class="article__announce-text">伊丽莎白二世可能在 40 年前第一次访问加利福尼亚时被一名男子暗杀，该男子的女儿在北爱尔兰冲突期间被杀。联邦调查局事先知道了他的意图，这次旅行平安无事。 </div></div><div class="article__body"><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text"> 1983 年 2 月，伊丽莎白二世和她的丈夫菲利普亲王从加利福尼亚开始对美国进行首次正式访问。当时，女王在前往洛杉矶之前访问了圣地亚哥，在那里她会见了当时的市长汤姆布拉德利。在圣巴巴拉，女王会见了美国第 40 任总统罗纳德里根。她还访问了旧金山、萨克拉门托、优胜美地和西雅图等城市。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text"><strong>但直到现在才发现，这次旅行差点以悲剧收场。</strong></div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">在伊丽莎白和菲利普亲王访问加利福尼亚之前大约一个月，一名旧金山警察告诉联邦调查局，他知道有一个人想为他的女儿报仇，他的女儿“在北爱尔兰被橡皮子弹杀死了”。警察在一家爱尔兰酒吧认识了比男人。 </div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="quote"><div class="article__quote"><div class="article__quote-text"><p> “他打算试图伤害伊丽莎白女王，他会通过将一些物体从金门大桥上扔到在下面航行的皇家游艇不列颠尼亚号上来做到这一点，或者会在伊丽莎白女王访问约塞米蒂国家公园时试图杀死她，”文档读取。 </p></div><div class="article__quote-info"><div class="elem-info"><div class="elem-info__share"><div class="share" data-id="1110618206" data-url="https://sputnikglobe.com/20230526/fbi-reveals-1983-plot-to-assassinate-queen-elizabeth-ii-during-us-visit-1110618206.html?share-block=1110618612" data-title="&amp;quot;He was going to attempt to harm Queen Elizabeth and would do this either by dropping some object off the Golden Gate Bridge onto the Royal Yacht Britannia when it sails underneath, or would attempt to kill Queen Elizabeth when she visited Yosemite National Park,&amp;quot; the document reads."></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">英国媒体指出，目前尚不清楚当时具体采取了哪些措施来确保伊丽莎白二世的安全，但已知的是要求“在游艇靠近时关闭金门大桥上的人行道”。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">调查结果还突出了 1976 年美国二百周年庆典期间发生的一件事，当时已故女王在纽约市。一名驾驶小型飞机飞越炮台公园的飞行员举着一个牌子，上面写着：“英格兰，滚出爱尔兰。”针对这一挑衅行为，联邦调查局向飞行员发出了传票。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">新发布的报告详细说明了联邦调查局如何密切关注对她生命的任何潜在威胁，女王与爱尔兰动荡的家庭关系也得到了强调。 </div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="vrez"><div class="article__vrez"><div class="article__vrez-text"><p>伊丽莎白的第二代堂兄蒙巴顿勋爵于 1979 年在爱尔兰共和国斯莱戈郡海岸附近的爱尔兰共和军爆炸案中丧生。这一具体事件可能加剧了她随后访问美国期间对安全的担忧。</p></div></div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">伊丽莎白被描述为对肯塔基州的喜爱，因为已故君主多次访问该州以享受肯塔基赛马等马术赛事。在 1991 年的国事访问期间，她计划与乔治·H·布什总统一起观看巴尔的摩金莺队的棒球比赛。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">当时，联邦调查局警告特勤局“爱尔兰团体”计划在体育场举行抗议活动，并透露其中一个团体已经预订了一大块看台门票。还有人指出，在她前往肯塔基州期间，特工们承认爱尔兰共和军的威胁“无处不在”。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">虽然发布的文件提供了宝贵的见解，但表明可能存在其他记录。目前尚不清楚这些额外文件何时会公开。</div></div></div> ]]>;</description><pubDate> Fri, 26 May 2023 22:20:09 GMT</pubDate><guid ispermalink="false"> https://sputniknews.com/20230526/fbi-reveals-1983-plot-to-assassinate-queen-elizabeth-ii-during-us-visit-1110618206.html</guid><link/> https://sputniknews.com/20230526/fbi-reveals-1983-plot-to-assassinate-queen-elizabeth-ii-during-us-visit-1110618206.html<category>超越政治</category><category>病毒性的</category><category>我们</category><category>英国女王伊丽莎白二世</category><category>联邦调查局</category><category>菲利普亲王</category><category>罗纳德里根</category><category>北爱尔兰</category><category>金门大桥</category><category>正式访问</category></item><item><title><![CDATA[10 Officers Singled Out for Possible Charges in US Navy Report on SEALs Training Death]]></title><description><![CDATA[<div class="article__header"><div class="article__announce"><div class="media" data-media-tipe="ar16x9"><div class="media__size"><div class="photoview__open" data-photoview-group="1110619038" data-photoview-src="https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/102303/87/1023038728_0:0:1024:680_1440x900_80_0_1_c754a9e8f30d4eeba341f3cfa94a2145.jpg?source-sid=flickr" data-photoview-image-id="1023038727" data-photoview-sharelink="https://sputnikglobe.com/20230526/10-officers-singled-out-for-possible-charges-in-us-navy-report-on-seals-training-death-1110619038.html?share-img=1023038727"><noindex><div class="photoview__open-info"> <span class="photoview__copyright">© Flickr / Michelle Kapica for US Navy</span> <span class="photoview__desc-text">SEAL qualification training (SQT) 学生在彭德尔顿营地 100、200 和 300 码的 36 轮射击测试中瞄准。</span> </div></noindex><img media-type="ar16x9" data-source-sid="flickr" alt="SEAL qualification training (SQT) students take aim during a 36-round shooting test ranging from 100, 200 and 300 yards at Camp Pendleton.  - Sputnik International, 1920, 26.05.2023" title="海豹突击队资格训练 (SQT) 学生在彭德尔顿营地进行 100、200 和 300 码范围内的 36 轮射击测试期间进行瞄准。" src="https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/102303/87/1023038728_0:0:1024:577_1920x0_80_0_0_c83fd991aae24d689ecb5fb2f45979ce.jpg" decoding="async" width="1920" height="1080" srcset="https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/102303/87/1023038728_0:0:1024:577_640x0_80_0_0_fb66f033f4cc6c75fd3795ee5c31396a.jpg 640w,https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/102303/87/1023038728_0:0:1024:577_1280x0_80_0_0_79cf849e213a773802103120b2b7bdf8.jpg 1280w,https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/102303/87/1023038728_0:0:1024:577_1920x0_80_0_0_c83fd991aae24d689ecb5fb2f45979ce.jpg 1920w" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></div></div><div class="media__copyright " data-nosnippet=""><div class="media__copyright-item m-copyright"> © Flickr / Michelle Kapica 美国海军</div></div></div></div><div class="article__messengers"><div class="flex-align_center"><span class="article__google-news__label"></span></div><div class="flex-align_center"></div><div class="article__telegram-news flex-align_center"><span class="article__google-news__label">订阅</span></div><div class="flex-align_center"><div class="article__telegram-button"><a href="https://t.me/SputnikInt" title="国际的" class="" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">国际的</a></div><div class="article__telegram-button"><a href="https://telegram.me/sputniknewsindia" title="印度" class="" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">印度</a></div><div class="article__telegram-button"><a href="https://t.me/sputnik_africa" title="非洲" class="" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">非洲</a></div></div></div><div class="article__author"><div class="article__author-item"><div class="article__author-wrapper"><div class="article__author-info"><div class="article__author-name">芳汀嘉迪尼耶</div><div class="article__author-links"><a class="m-color-main" href="https://sputniknews.com/author_gardinier_fantine/" title="所有材料">所有材料</a></div></div></div></div></div><div class="article__announce-text">周四发布了一份严厉的美国海军报告，指出 10 名军官因所谓的“近乎完美的风暴”的失败而导致去年海豹突击队训练课程中的海员凯尔马伦死亡。 </div></div><div class="article__body"><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">海军教育和训练司令部发布<u><a href="https://int.nyt.com/data/documenttools/foia-release-25-may-2023-netc-final-report-redacted/516766336d204ac3/full.pdf" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener">的报告中</a></u>，这十名军官中的大多数人的名字都被删掉了，目前还没有对他们提出指控。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">被点名的人包括海军特种作战训练中心准将布赖恩·德雷克斯勒上尉和训练司令部首席医疗官埃里克·拉米博士。两人都因未能履行职责而被重新分配。 </div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="quote"><div class="article__quote"><div class="article__quote-text">报告称：“调查显示，对旨在确保学生安全的广泛重要投入存在一定程度的自满和关注不足。”这包括教师的做法、医务人员的准备情况，以及针对在课程中苦苦挣扎的学生滥用提高成绩药物的筛查。 </div><div class="article__quote-info"><div class="elem-info"><div class="elem-info__share"><div class="share" data-id="1110619038" data-url="https://sputnikglobe.com/20230526/10-officers-singled-out-for-possible-charges-in-us-navy-report-on-seals-training-death-1110619038.html?share-block=1110619040" data-title="“The investigation revealed a degree of complacency and insufficient attentiveness to a wide range of important inputs meant to keep the students safe,” the report said. That included the practices of instructors, the readiness of medical staff, and screenings against the abuse of performance-enhancing drugs used by students struggling with the course."></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">该报告发现，医疗监督和护理“组织不善、整合不善、领导不善，使候选人面临重大风险”，导致越来越多的学生住院甚至死亡，正如马伦在 2022 年 2 月所做的那样。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">马伦是近年来可怕的培训课程中的第 11 例此类死亡事件，该课程一直非常困难，通常只有 30% 的参加者有望毕业。然而，在 2021 年新领导上任后，毕业率进一步下滑。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">据报道，当时的学校指挥官休·W·霍华德少将告诉下属，如果没有人毕业也没关系。 </div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="quote"><div class="article__quote"><div class="article__quote-text"> “零在护堤上是一个不错的数字；保持标准，”据报道他告诉他们。 </div><div class="article__quote-info"><div class="elem-info"><div class="elem-info__share"><div class="share" data-id="1110619038" data-url="https://sputnikglobe.com/20230526/10-officers-singled-out-for-possible-charges-in-us-navy-report-on-seals-training-death-1110619038.html?share-block=1110619045" data-title="&quot;Zero is an okay number on the berm; hold the standard,” he reportedly told them."></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">该报告批评教官缺乏经验或训练，再加上更严厉的训练，导致他们认为自己不是在组建新的海豹突击队，而是“追赶群雄”以“淘汰”弱者的执法者。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">据报道，当时负责该课程的指挥官布拉德利·吉尔里上尉“认为，人员流失问题的主要原因是当代人的精神韧性较差。” </div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="quote"><div class="article__quote"><div class="article__quote-text">报告称，“允许以这种方式继续执行课程，同时伴随着历史性、快速和重大的减员变化表明监督不足”。 </div><div class="article__quote-info"><div class="elem-info"><div class="elem-info__share"><div class="share" data-id="1110619038" data-url="https://sputnikglobe.com/20230526/10-officers-singled-out-for-possible-charges-in-us-navy-report-on-seals-training-death-1110619038.html?share-block=1110619048" data-title="“Allowing continued execution of the curriculum in this manner while accompanied by historic, rapid and significant changes to attrition demonstrated insufficient oversight” by Geary, the report said."></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">该报告将难度的升级称为“强度蠕变”，称教师将学生“推向了可接受范围的尽头”，使疲惫、疾病和受伤变得更加普遍。 </div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="vrez"><div class="article__vrez"><div class="article__vrez-text"><p>事实上，在所谓“地狱周”的大部分时间里，马伦一直患有肺炎和其他疾病。就在马伦呼吸困难时，医务人员建议其他学生不要拨打 9-1-1，声称这会干扰他们的训练。</p></div></div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">美国一家报纸在 Mullen 死后进行的一项调查发现，教师让学生长时间泡在冷水里，不让他们睡觉，殴打他们，不让他们接受医疗，除非他们退出课程。学生们也参与了虐待，批评者说这使得课程只不过是一种欺凌仪式。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">在他死后，海军人员在他的车里发现了提高成绩的药物，包括睾酮和人体生长激素。然而，海军特种作战司令部在 10 月份的一份报告中表示，这名 24 岁的海员“在执行任务时死亡，而不是由于他自己的不当行为”。</div></div></div> ]]>;</description><pubDate> Fri, 26 May 2023 21:30:57 GMT</pubDate><guid ispermalink="false"> https://sputniknews.com/20230526/10-officers-singled-out-for-possible-charges-in-us-navy-report-on-seals-training-death-1110619038.html</guid><link/> https://sputniknews.com/20230526/10-officers-singled-out-for-possible-charges-in-us-navy-report-on-seals-training-death-1110619038.html<category>军队</category><category>美国海豹突击队</category><category>死亡</category><category>美国海军</category><category>报告</category></item></channel></rss>